  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, we saw the first thing was that I saw trains and trains and trains loaded with soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very huge in my eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, I knew that they sent only the high, I mean, a meter, 80 or so--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--soldiers to make an impression.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Mahrisch-Ostrau was even one day before Prague occupied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Prague was a day later occupied.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember there were many refugees from Slovakia and other places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even one uncle came and was very nervous, and said the German are occupying Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a great tension, and he was running away to another place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But for us children, it was interesting what's happening We were living could not so far away from the railway station that was looking there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we went out in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were some tanks and slogans, Recht gehen links ubertrat, which means, Sonny, go right and cross on the left side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What did it meant?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Czechoslovakia, it was different, like today, still in England, everything was on the left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, so they changed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the first things was right and left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The second thing was, as a child, we run to the post office, and we wanted to get the first issue of--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The new stamps.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the stamp, I got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was 'die Stadt der schwarzen Diamanten dank den Fuhrer fur ihre befreiung.' Which meant the city, or the town, of the black diamonds, coal, thanks the Fuhrer for their liberation.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went to the streets and saw tanks, and we touched them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually, it was armored cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because in the rumors, they said, oh, no, they are not really armored.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The German don't have so much armors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are from cartoon.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
